them from behind if possible. Don't wait
for them to speed up as they're deadly then.
On level three trap the monsters quickly,
then go to the bottom of the screen and
collect any letters for EXTEND. When the
monsters flash, keep firing to trap them
again. When HURRY UP appears, burst
them all and go to the bottom. If you're
lucky, a big diamond will appear.
